    "description": "你是一个年轻的转基因霸王龙之子，生活在后世界末日的东京，他在对人类废墟的迷恋和服从过度保护的父亲之间左右为难。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/4951994b0e32afe0ea94e8d2352a54d4.poster.avif?t=1732832566\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/4951994b0e32afe0ea94e8d2352a54d4.webm?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/4951994b0e32afe0ea94e8d2352a54d4.mp4?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>克服障碍时要保持隐秘和聪明。 <br>您将做出多种选择来解决旅途中遇到的问题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/2f915eadb112d410f081fd056792971c.poster.avif?t=1732832566\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/2f915eadb112d410f081fd056792971c.webm?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/2f915eadb112d410f081fd056792971c.mp4?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你为生存而战时，要敏捷而敏锐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/ddf2cc6d666bc550ebf92b59a91c8b22.poster.avif?t=1732832566\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/ddf2cc6d666bc550ebf92b59a91c8b22.webm?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/ddf2cc6d666bc550ebf92b59a91c8b22.mp4?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索世界各地的居民并与之互动，欣赏风景如画的未来派摩天大楼以及长满茂密植被的传统寺庙。 <br><br>在恐龙慢慢回归原始本能的世界里，本能与智力是一个核心冲突。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/94b8d6c24382c627bd8e5e7d173359bf.poster.avif?t=1732832566\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/94b8d6c24382c627bd8e5e7d173359bf.webm?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/94b8d6c24382c627bd8e5e7d173359bf.mp4?t=1732832566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过史诗般的电影过场动画探索情感叙事的深度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183080/extras/GIF_ToriYamaCinematic.gif?t=1732832566\" /></span><br>本杰明·穆洛 (Benjamin Mulot) 与 Floating Rock Studio 位于新西兰的小而强大的团队共同创作了《Kyoryu》，向他已故的父亲以及他们在恐龙上建立的关系致敬。",
